Final project (milestone 1)

Answer the questions in REPORT.txt. All team members should submit. Identical
copies are ok.

COMPILE: 
Linux - 
g++ *.cpp $(sdl2-config --cflags --libs)

Mac - 
g++ *.cpp -I/opt/homebrew/include -L/opt/homebrew/lib -lSDL2

RUN:
./a.out <rom.gb>

HEADLESS (no GUI):
./a.out <rom.gb> --headless
